#  Billing Application

A simple web-based billing application to manage customer bills and calculate totals in real-time.

---

##  Features

- Add and remove items dynamically
- Auto calculate total amount
- Responsive and user-friendly interface
- Simple HTML, CSS, and JavaScript-based project

---

##  Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

